  ('37017', 428, 5473, 'I''d want it to feel less like a scoreboard and more like a partner—anticipating rough patches, offering flexible support, and recognizing progress even when it''s messy. Instead of generic alerts and fees, I''d want personalized guidance that actually helps me make better decisions in the moment, not just react after the fact', 'Millennial', 'Male', '$125,000 to $149,999', 'Northeast', 'Parent', 'm_2026_04', '2026-04'),
